title: Hank Snow - 218 Songs
description:
Let's have an endurance contest between rare classic country of Hank Snow and rare classic jazz of the Roaring Twenties. First one down to a single seeder gets retired.

Update: "Roaring Twenties" is way ahead. 
It looks like classic jazz fans are more willing to be helpful 
than classic country fans.

Unless "Hank Snow - 218 Songs" gets better support I guess there's no point in offering more country torrents.

Update: Great! "Hank Snow - 218 Songs" has pulled ahead and looks like it might stay around for your kids.

So I better upload Emmylou.
